    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Check out this dependable daily driver that's ready for its next adventure! This car is in fair condition, showing some honest wear and tear from its years of reliable service, but it still has plenty of life left in it. It's a fantastic, budget-friendly option for someone who prioritizes function and character over a showroom finish. If you're looking for a solid vehicle with a proven track record, this is the one for you!",
