    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience the perfect blend of performance and reliability with this meticulously maintained professional-grade vehicle. This car stands as a testament to quality ownership, featuring a refined interior and a robust mechanical profile that ensures a smooth, confident drive. Rigorously inspected to meet our exacting standards, it offers an exceptional balance of comfort and long-term value. Turn-key ready for its next discerning owner, this is a premier opportunity to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that delivers both prestige and peace of mind.",
      "price": 36800.0,
